snippet: Three peacekeepers serving in the joint United Nations-African Union force in the Darfur region have been killed in an attack by gunmen, officials said.
abstract: Three peacekeepers serving in the joint United Nations-African Union force in the Darfur region of Sudan are killed in an attack by gunmen.
